messageBody:
Eytan,

You could try Clover, I have been using the 0.6beta a bit and it seems
to give clear results.

Haven't tried the 1.0eval yet though.

Their website is quite good, explains what it is all about, and gives
some example outputs for common open-source software.

http://www.thecortex.net/clover/

Andy.
